rows.label: qst560207_msg0001
rows.name:
I am a Nopon who travels the world
in search of people who will tell me
thrilling adventure stories, mo.

rows.label: qst560207_msg0002
rows.name:
To meet in a place like
this, you must have had
an amazing adventure, mo.

rows.label: qst560207_msg0003
rows.name: Please, tell me about it, mo.

rows.label: qst560207_msg0004
rows.name: Trade for a Master Evasion Mod?

rows.label: qst560207_msg0101
rows.name:
Thank you for the wonderful
adventure story, mo.

rows.label: qst560207_msg0102
rows.name:
As a reward, I'll give you a
special item I received long
ago from a strange Nopon, mo.

rows.label: qst560207_msg0207
rows.name:
If you change your mind, I
hope you'll come back to tell
me your adventure story, mo.

rows.label: qst560207_msg0203
rows.name: I'll be waiting here forever, mo.
